%20Trump's%20tariff%20plan%20will%20have%20drastic%20economic%20effects.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20risk%20of%20the%20global%20economy%20falling%20into%20a%20recession%20has%20increased%20from%2040%25%20to%2060%25%2C%20they%20warned.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20restrictive%20trade%20policy%20also%20risks%20supply-side%20damage%20that'll%20lower%20US%20growth%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJP%20Morgan's%20chief%20global%20economist%20has%20a%20bleak%20outlook%20on%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-mexico-canada-tariffs-economic-uncertainty-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaggressive%20tariff%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20blood.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20research%20note%20to%20clients%20published%20on%20Thursday%2C%20JP%20Morgan's%20Bruce%20Kasman%2C%20along%20with%20several%20other%20company%20economists%2C%20warned%20that%20the%20risk%20of%20the%20global%20economy%20falling%20into%20a%20recession%20has%20increased%20from%2040%25%20to%2060%25%20in%20response%20to%20Wednesday's%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariff%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20on%20Wednesday%20announced%20sweeping%2010%25%20tariffs%20on%20goods%20from%20any%20country%20imported%20into%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20even%20higher%20tariffs%20for%2060%20trading%20partners%20with%20a%20persistent%20trade%20deficit%20with%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wide-reaching%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20impact%20countries%20including%20China%20and%20Japan%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20and%20territories%20near%20Antarctica%C2%A0inhabited%20only%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-liberation-day-tariffs-hit-uninhabited-antarctic-islands-penguins-australia-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epenguins%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Eare%20