20trade%20deficit%20with%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wide-reaching%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20impact%20countries%20including%20China%20and%20Japan%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20and%20territories%20near%20Antarctica%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-liberation-day-tariffs-hit-uninhabited-antarctic-islands-penguins-australia-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einhabited%20only%20by%20penguins%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecome%20in%20addition%20to%20existing%20tariffs%20against%20the%20United%20States'%20top%20trade%20partners%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-canada-mexico-missing-from-donald-trump-reciprocal-tariff-chart-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECanada%20and%20Mexico%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20consumers%2C%C2%A0the%20increased%20import%20costs%20caused%20by%20Trump's%20aggressive%20tariff%20plan%20are%20expected%20to%20result%20in%20higher%20prices%20for%20everything%20from%20pantry%20staples%20like%20coffee%20and%20sugar%20to%20apparel%20and%20larger%20purchases%20like%20cars%20and%20appliances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErnie%20Tedeschi%2C%20the%20director%20of%20economics%20at%20the%20Budget%20Lab%20at%20Yale%2C%20said%20the%20price%20hikes%20are%20expected%20to%20increase%20the%20overall%20price%20level%20of%20goods%20in%20the%20United%20States%20by%202.3%25%2C%20costing%20the%20average%20consumer%20household%20about%20%243%2C800%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETedeschi%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20existing%20tariffs%20against%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20alone%20account%20for%20an%20expected%201%25%20price%20increase%20of%20about%20%241%2C700%20per%20household.%20The%20%26quot%3BLiberation%20Day%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20announced%20Wednesday%20are%20expected%20to%20result%20in%20a%20further%201.3%25%20hike%2C%20or%20%242%2C100%20per%20household.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%201.3%25%20may%20not%20sound%20like%20a%20lot%20to%20the%20normal%20person%2C%20but%20%242%2C100%20is%20a%20meaningful%20amount%2C%26quot%3B%20Tedeschi%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20of%20course%2C%20that's%20an%20average%2C%20so%20if%20you%20open%20up%20the%20hood%20to%20that%20number%2C%20there's%20a%20distribution%20beneath%20that%20number.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2282dfe0a3-0acb-4c4b-8936-24c652576417%5C%22%3EPrice%20hikes%20on%20pantry%20staples%20and%20produce%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exact%20intention%20behind%20Trump's%20tariff%20plan%20remains%20unclear%20%E2%80%94%20the%20president%20says%20his%20main%20goal%20is%20to%20bring%20manufacturing%20jobs%20back%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20but%20some%20analysts%20suspect%20he%20may%20be%20trying%20to%20trigger%20a%20recession%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fis-trump-crashing-the-economy-on-purpose-trade-war-tariffs-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereduce%20interest%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20purposely%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-tariffs-trade-war-trump-recession-stagflation-economy-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20stock%20market%20has%20tanked%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20response%20to%20the%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImports%20from%20some%20countries%20will%20be%20hit%20with%20higher%20tariffs%20than%20others%2C%20driving%20uneven%20price%20hikes%20across%20industries.%20For%20example%2C%20China%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0which%20largely%20imports%20machinery%20and%20appliances%2C%20furniture%2C%20toys%2C%20and%20electronics%20to%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewill%20be%20subject%20to%20a%2054%25%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-plan-external-revenue-service-imports-impact-consumers-economy-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariff%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20combining%20the%20new%20tariffs%20(34%25)%20with%20ones%20that%20have%20been%20previously%20announced.%20Goods%20from%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20which%20primarily%20imports%20medical%20and%20pharmaceutical%20products%20and%20motor%20vehicles%2C%20will%20be%20subject%20to%20a%20new%2020%25%20tariff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETedeschi%20said%20the%20cost%20of%20clothing%20items%20is%20expected%20to%20increase%20by%20about%208%25.%20He%20added%20that%20pantry%20staples%20like%20sugar%20and%20coffee%20are%20expected%20to%20increase%20in%20price%20by%20about%201.3%25%2C%20while%20fresh%20produce%20is%20likely%20to%20increase%20by%20about%202.2%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20luxury%20of%20eating%20our%20favorite%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20regardless%20of%20the%20season%20is%20based%20on%20global%20imports%20with%20much%20coming%20from%20Central%20and%20South%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20Margaret%20Kidd%2C%20an%20instructional%20associate%20professor%20of%20supply%20chain%20and%20logistics%20technology%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Houston%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BTariffs%20will%20make%20many%20of%20these%20staples%20unaffordable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States-Mexico-Canada%20Agreement%2C%20which%20replaced%20the%20North%20American%20Free%20Trade%20Agreement%20in%202020%2C%20maintains%20NAFTA's%20zero-tariff%20treatment%20for%20most%20agricultural%20products%2C%20textiles%2C%20apparel%2C%20and%20other%20goods%20that%20meet%20the%20trade%20agreement's%20rules%20of%20origin.%20But%20while%20the%20United%20States%20gets%20much%20of%20its%20produce%20from%20neighboring%20Mexico%20tariff-free%2C%20including%20tomatoes%2C%20avocados%2C%20and%20strawberries%2C%20other%20imports%20will%20face%20new%20price%20hikes%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0like%20grapes%20from%20Peru%20or%20bananas%20and%20mangoes%20from%20the%20Philippines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20USMCA%20is%20still%20in%20effect%2C%20so%20there%20are%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20still%20covered%20under%20the%20deal%20and%20are%20tariff-free%2C%20but%20then%20some%20of%20them%2C%20they%20are%20not%20covered%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20Tang%2C%20a%20UCLA%20professor%20who's%20an%20expert%20in%20global%20supply%20chain%20management%20and%20the%20impact%20of%20regulatory%20policies%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aaf82db9-9819-4a9a-8dd4-bef67bcb088a%5C%22%3EStockpiling%20and%20substitutions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20consumers%20and%20businesses%20alike%20will%20try%20to%20find%20substitutions.%20Still%2C%20Tedeschi%20said%20it%20takes%20time%20to%20carve%20out%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretailers-small-businesses-react-trump-trade-tariffs-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupply%20chain%3C%2Fa%3E%20routes%2C%20for%20stores%20to%20expand%20their%20offerings%2C%20and%20for%20customers%20to%20find%20suitable%20alternatives%20to%20their%20typical%20favorites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20you%20may%2C%20literally%20and%20figuratively%2C%20eat%20the%20price%20increase%20in%20the%20short%20run%2C%20as%20you're%20figuring%20out%20what%20a%20proper%20substitute%20is%2C%20but%20there%20are%20areas%20where%20there%20will%20be%20substitutions%20available%2C%26quot%3B%20Tedeschi%20said.%20%26quot%3BLet's%20say%20coffee%2C%20for%20example%2C%20imported%20from%20Colombia.%20If%20Starbucks%20has%20a%20supply%20chain%20agreement%20with%20Colombia%2C%20over%20time%2C%20they'll%20be%20able%20to%20shift%20that%20to%20another%20country%20or%20another%20supplier%20to%20mitigate%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20tariff%2C%20perhaps.%20Whereas%2C%20in%20the%20short%20run%2C%20like%2C%20in%20a%20month%2C%20Starbucks%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20that%2C%20so%20if%20you%20want%20your%20latte%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20pay%20extra.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%2C%20like%20%26quot%3BShark%20Tank%26quot%3B%20star%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-buy-lots-consumables-now-after-trump-tariff-rollout-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMark%20Cuban%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20suggested%20Americans%20start%20stockpiling%20goods%20now%20to%20avoid%20price%20hikes.%20They%20say%20retailers%20may%20raise%20prices%20and%20%26quot%3Bblame%20it%20on%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20even%20if%20their%20goods%20are%20US-made.%20While%20the%20experts%20who%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20say%20that%20may%20be%20true%2C%20panic%20buying%20might%20further%20hurt%20supply%20chains%20and%20cause%20prices%20to%20go%20up%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20kind%20of%20shift%20in%20demand%20would%20actually%20exacerbate%20this%20price%20increase%2C%26quot%3B%20Tang%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20demand%20is%20more%20stable%2C%20then%20the%20price%20is%20more%20stable.%20If%20everyone%20starts%20stocking%20up%20on%20toothpaste%20and%20toilet%20paper%2C%20the%20prices%20go%20higher.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d59fec5-0830-49ef-b0ab-ee79f146e23e%5C%22%3ELow-income%20households%20will%20bear%20the%20brunt%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20just%20the%20immediate%20impact%20on%20everyday%20consumable%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Consumer%20Technology%20Association%20estimated%20in%20a%20January%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fshop.cta.tech%2Fproducts%2Fhow-the-proposed-trump-tariffs-increase-prices-for-consumer-technology-products-january-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Trump's%20tariffs%20could%20increase%20the%20price%20of%20laptops%20and%20tablets%20by%2046-68%25%2C%20video%20game%20consoles%20by%2040-58%25%2C%20and%20smartphones%20by%2026-37%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-stock-price-trump-auto-tariffs-trade-war-tech-stocks-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECar%20imports%20will%20see%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20upward%20of%2025%25%2C%20which%20could%20translate%20to%20%2412%2C000%20or%20more%20based%20on%20an%20average%20car%20price%20of%20%2448%2C000.%20Some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%