iatimes.com%2Findia%2Fin-counter-to-yunuss-remark-pm-modi-says-northeast-integral-to-bimstec%2Farticleshow%2F119956816.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Waqf%20Bill%20Passed%20By%20Rajya%20Sabha%20With%20128%20Votes%20For%2C%2095%20Against%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Waqf%20bill%2C%20after%20a%20smooth%20passage%20through%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20breezed%20through%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2024%20hours%20later%2C%20after%20yet%20another%20marathon%20debate.%20On%20its%20way%2C%20it%20exposed%20a%20chink%20in%20the%20armour%20of%20the%20parties%20opposing%20the%20bill.%20The%20voting%20was%20128%20votes%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20bill%20and%2095%20against.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20few%20hours%20before%20the%20voting%2C%20Naveen%20Patkaik's%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20opened%20the%20gates%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bconscience%20vote'%20telling%20its%20seven%20upper%20house%20MPs%20that%20they%20would%20not%20be%20bound%20by%20a%20whip%20and%20could%20vote%20for%20whichever%20side%20they%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party's%20senior%20leader%20Sasmit%20Patra%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20said%20they%20took%20that%20view%20after%20taking%20into%20consideration%20the%20sentiments%20of%20%26quot%3Bdifferent%20sections%20of%20the%20Minority%20communities%20regarding%20the%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Debate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arguments%2C%20though%2C%20were%20on%20expected%20lines.%20Minorities%20affairs%20minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%2C%20opening%20the%20debate%2C%20dismissed%20allegations%20that%20the%20bill%20would%20harm%20Muslim%20interests%20and%20asserted%20that%20non-Muslims%20cannot%20interfere%20in%20the%20Waqf%20Board's%20affairs%20as%20its%20management%2C%20creation%2C%20and%20beneficiaries%20would%20remain%20exclusively%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasizing%20his%20argument%20that%20the%20bill%20is%20not%20about%20religion%20but%20property%20and%20its%20management%20and%20aims%20to%20root%20out%20corruption%2C%20he%20said%20proof%20of%20ownership%20will%20now%20be%20required%20before%20a%20property%20is%20declared%20Waqf.%20This%2C%20he%20added%2C%20will%20eliminate%20the%20previous%20provision%20where%20any%20claim%20by%20the%20Waqf%20Board%20automatically%20led%20to%20its%20designation%20as%20Waqf%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rijiju%20and%20Union%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20yesterday%20listed%20properties%20that%20were%20labelled%20Wakf%2C%20among%20them%20properties%20in%20Delhi's%20Lutyens%20zone%2C%20a%20400-year-old%20temple%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20land%20for%20a%20five-star%20establishment%20and%20even%20the%20old%20parliament%20building.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress's%20Syed%20Naseer%20Hussain%2C%20who%20responded%20to%20Mr%20Rijiju%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20creating%20confusion%20about%20123%20properties.%20They%20are%20either%20masjids%2C%20burial%20grounds%20or%20dargahs%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20submit%20a%20list%20of%20those%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20British%20occupied%20Lutyens'%20Delhi%2C%20these%20properties%20were%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Waqf%20by%20them%20after%20construction%20of%20the%20area.%20These%20properties%20are%20with%20the%20Waqf.%20These%20were%20the%20ones%20that%20are%20being%20referred%20to%20by%20them%20in%20relation%20to%202013%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20an%20acrimonious%20exchange%20between%20Mr%20Hussain%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20today%2C%20when%20the%20former%20questioned%20the%20BJP%20argument%20that%20at%20under%20the%20existing%20Waqf%20Act%2C%20people%20can't%20move%20court%20if%20they%20are%20aggrieved%20with%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20Tribunal.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20false.%20How%20are%20there%20so%20many%20pending%20cases%20in%20the%20High%20Court%20and%20Supreme%20Court%20if%20none%20could%20move%20court%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(the%20Congress)%20did%20not%20keep%20a%20provision%20for%20a%20civil%20suit%2C%20which%20has%20a%20wide%20purview%2C%20in%20the%20court%20in%20the%202013%20Act.%20They%20only%20have%20a%20provision%20for%20writ%20jurisdiction%20in%20the%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20has%20a%20very%20limited%20purview%2C%26quot%3B%20retorted%20Mr%20Shah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20bill%2C%20Union%20Minister%20JP%20Nadda%20accused%20the%20Opposition%20of%20attempting%20to%20divert%20and%20derail%20the%20issue%20and%20asserted%20that%20it%20would%20be%20good%20if%20they%20paid%20attention%20to%20the%20deprived%20sections%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20He%20also%20questioned%20why%20India%20cannot%20make%20changes%20when%20Muslim%20nations%20are%20making%20Waqf%20properties%20transparent%20and%20digitized%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress's%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20the%20bill%20should%20not%20be%20made%20into%20a%20prestige%20issue.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20you%20(government)%20are%20doing%20is%20not%20good.%20This%20will%20lead%20to%20disputes%20in%20the%20country.%20You%20are%20sowing%20seeds%20for%20disputes...%20I%20appeal%20to%20the%20Home%20Minister%20to%20withdraw%20this.%20What%20is%20the%20harm%20in%20rectifying%20the%20errors%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20what%20he%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomparative%20statement%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20the%20Bill%20was%20passed%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20with%20288%20Ayes%20and%20232%20Noes.%20%26quot%3BDid%20everyone%20accept%20it%3F%20This%20means%20that%20there%20are%20drawbacks%20(in%20the%20Bill).%20You%20should%20see%20this...%20If%20you%20go%20by%20'jiski%20laathi%20uski%20bhains'%2C%20this%20will%20not%20be%20good%20for%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20Centre%20over%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20legislation%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWhy%20two%20non-Muslims%20are%20required%20(to%20be%20part%20of%20Waqf%20board)%3F%20In%20Tirupati%2C%20do%20you%20keep%20any%20Muslims%3F%20Are%20there%20Muslim%20members%20in%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20Trust%3F%20Let%20alone%20Muslims%2C%20you%20won't%20put%20a%20Dalit%20Hindu%20like%20me%20also%20there.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20words%20echoed%20AIMIM%20leader%20Imtiaz%20Jaleel%2C%20who%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20non-Muslims%20are%20going%20to%20be%20appointed%20on%20the%20Waqf%20Board%2C%20are%20they%20going%20to%20include%20Imtiaz%20Jaleel%20in%20Shirdi%20Saibaba%20(temple)%20trust%20or%20Tirupati%20temple%20trust.%20If%20such%20a%20board%20comes%20up%20for%20the%20Sikh%20community%2C%20no%20non-Sikh%20can%20be%20appointed.%20So%2C%20why%20such%20things%20are%20for%20the%20Waqf%20Board%20only%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Next%20For%20The%20Bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20had%20passed%20the%20bill%20with%20a%20288-232%20vote%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Thursday%20after%20a%20debate%20lasting%20over%2012%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20legislation%20--%20which%20will%20be%20sent%20for%20President's%20sign-off%20next%20--%20aims%20to%20amend%20the%201995%20law%20governing%20Waqf%20properties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Contentious%20Provisions%20of%20Waqf%20Bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contentious%20provisions%20in%20the%20amended%20bill%20include%20mandatory%20inclusion%20of%20two%20non-Muslim%20members%20in%20the%20Central%20Waqf%20Council%20and%20Waqf%20Boards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20the%20stipulation%20that%20only%20individuals%20who%20practiced%20Islam%20for%20at%20least%20five%20years%20can%20donate%20properties%20to%20Waqf.%20The%20Opposition%20has%20questioned%20how%20the%20government%20intends%20to%20determine%20who%20a%20practicing%20Muslim%20is.%20They%20have%20also%20argued%20that%20barring%20converts%20from%20making%20donations%20is%20an%20interference%20in%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20to%20practice%20religion%20and%20the%20law%20on%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20proposed%20law%2C%20government%20property%20identified%20as%20Waqf%20will%20cease%20to%20belong%20to%20it%20and%20the%20local%20Collector%20will%20determine%20its%20ownership.%20The%20bill%20also%20proposes%20that%20an%20officer%20above%20the%20rank%20of%20collector%20will%20investigate%20government%20properties%20claimed%20as%20Waqf.%20In%20case%20of%20disputes%2C%20the%20senior%20government%20official%20will%20have%20the%20final%20say%20on%20whether%20a%20property%20belongs%20to%20Waqf%20or%20the%20government.%20This%20replaces%20the%20existing%20system%20where%20such%20decisions%20are%20made%20by%20Waqf%20tribunals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20as%20well%20as%20a%20section%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20interprets%20it%20as%20a%20government%20move%20to%20gain%20control%20over%20Waqf%20properties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743715020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Flh4.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2Fvdyf-B8dGC9HNNJgRLnOtQgOTZuJS4tRhxzzFGSKwkhQEMqYTnol2fMYPkedqk3K8sU7gGuDQiuGRC3nO8tbuIlcGQ5wiii8kSnUDrC6XLW5yGhAAfAGwmn3W8B5oqCwsn-L%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-passed-by-rajya-sabha-with-128-votes-for-95-against-day-after-lok-sabha-cleared-it-8081809%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill%20passed%20by%20Rajya%20Sabha%20with%20128%20votes%20for%2C%2095%20against%2C%20day%20after%20Lok%20Sabha%20cleared%20it%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Grateful%20and%20honoured'%3A%20Tom%20Cruise%20pays%20tribute%20to%20Val%20Kilmer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743714978000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F3dd8%2