ly%20its%20biggest%20ad%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEric%20Haggstrom%2C%20director%20of%20market%20intelligence%20at%20Advertiser%20Perceptions%2C%20said%20the%20most%20immediate%20impact%20would%20be%20on%20quick-turn%20products%20like%20apparel%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-buy-lots-consumables-now-after-trump-tariff-rollout-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome%20goods%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20losers%20you're%20going%20to%20see%20right%20now%20are%20companies%20based%20on%20Chinese-based%20advertising%3A%20social%20media%20and%20retail%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAd%20analysts%20stressed%20that%20tariffs%20would%20affect%20every%20product%20category%20and%20ad%20seller%20because%20of%20the%20global%20nature%20of%20many%20supply%20chains.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-trump-tariffs-china-liberation-day-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20notably%2C%20will%20likely%20get%20hit%20hard%20because%20China%20is%20its%20biggest%20manufacturing%20hub.%20But%20the%20situation%20is%20so%20fluid%20that%20it's%20impossible%20to%20predict%20with%20any%20certainty%20at%20this%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20sector%20that%20doesn't%20get%20hit%20by%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Wieser%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20argued%20that%20Amazon%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20search%20ad-driven%20Google%20would%20be%20resilient%20because%20of%20their%20scale%2C%20measurability%2C%20and%20ability%20to%20drive%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20retail%20media%20outlets%20are%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nadja%20Bellan-White%2C%20CEO%20of%20%3Cspan%3EM%2BC%20Saatchi%20Group%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20adding%20that%20advertisers'%20expectations%20for%20performance%20guarantees%20will%20be%20greater%20than%20ever.%20%26quot%3BThey%20want%20to%20know%20if%20they%20spend%20X%20amount%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20get%20X%20result.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENewStreet%20Research%20analysts%20wrote%20that%20Pinterest%2C%20Reddit%2C%20and%20Snap%20would%20be%20the%20most%20challenged%20from%20an%20ad%20standpoint%20because%20they%20have%20smaller%20user%20bases%20than%20the%20likes%20of%20Meta.%20Reddit%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20strong%20user%20communities%20but%20a%20specific%20vibe%20that%20takes%20extra%20work%20for%20an%20advertiser%20to%20fit%20into.%20Big%20advertisers%20could%20retreat%20to%20the%20platforms%20they%20are%20most%20familiar%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tariffs%20upheaval%20comes%20as%20the%20ad%20industry%20prepares%20for%20its%20biggest%20showcase%20of%20the%20year%2C%20the%20television%20upfronts%2C%20when%20TV%20giants%20try%20to%20lock%20in%20large%20chunks%20of%20ad%20inventory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdvertisers%20are%20still%20going%20to%20want%20to%20lock%20in%20dollars%20when%20they%20need%20to%20run%20ads%20tied%20to%20product%20launches%2C%26quot%3B%20Haggstrom%20said.%20%26quot%3BAdvertisers%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20are%20able%20to%20place%20their%20advertising%20at%20the%20right%20time.%20But%20these%20negotiations%20might%20take%20longer%20due%20to%20the%20whole%20economic%20and%20fiscal%20situation.%20This%20is%20a%20pretty%20major%20shock.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELive%20sports%20is%20driving%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20TV%20market%20because%20of%20its%20big%2C%20reliable%2C%20and%20ad-friendly%20audience%2C%20which%20could%20benefit%20players%20like%20Disney%20and%20NBCUniversal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESports%20is%20the%20watchword%20for%20advertisers%20as%20they%20worry%20about%20political%20backlash%2C%20longtime%20ad%20industry%20player%20Michael%20Kassan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20safest%20place%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20view%20is%20that%20advertisers%20could%20be%20hesitant%20to%20lock%20themselves%20into%20big%20TV%20buy%20and%20could%20shift%20spendi