ow%2C%20meaning%20you%20can%20find%20the%20loft%20and%20firmness%20that%20works%20for%20you.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELoft%20is%20really%20just%20a%20fancy%20way%20to%20refer%20to%20your%20pillow's%20thickness.%20It%20is%20important%20because%20your%20pillow's%20height%20keeps%20your%20spine%20aligned%20through%20the%20night%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20sleeping%20position.%20Side%20sleepers%2C%20for%20example%2C%20need%20a%20loftier%20pillow%20to%20keep%20their%20neck%20supported.%20Stomach%20sleepers%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20can%20use%20a%20low-loft%20pillow%20to%20avoid%20neck%20and%20back%20pain%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20a%20low-loft%20pillow%20is%20three%20inches%20or%20less%2C%20while%20a%20medium-loft%20pillow%20is%20between%20three%20and%20five%20inches.%20A%20high-loft%20pillow%20is%20more%20than%20five%20inches%20tall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPillows%20with%20an%20adjustable%20loft%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-74965-20%26h%3Dfa3293b7c743cb3ca13b8ecdcc0df452d39f84a7eff7214b57e14ef11feab081%26postID%3D67ed6428b154b4859e632ce0%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fhow-to-choose-a-pillow%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fcoopsleepgoods.com%252Fproducts%252Fthe-original-pillow%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECoop%20Sleep%20Goods%20Original%20Pillow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20a%20versatile%20choice.%20By%20adding%20or%20removing%20fill%2C%20you%20can%20create%20the%20perfect%20loft%20for%20your%20sleep%20type%20and%20comfort%20preferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2297ffdc8f-cb08-4f97-9cd3-8da9bf958ed1%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Size%20and%20shape%5C%22%3ESize%20and%20shape%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20three%20main%20sizes%20of%20pillows%3A%20standard%2C%20queen%2C%20and%20king.%20Standard%20pillows%20are%2020%26quot%3B%20by%2026%26quot%3B%2C%20queen%20pillows%20are%2020%26quot%3B%20by%2030%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20king%20pillows%20are%2020%26quot%3B%20x%2036%26quot%3B.%20Pillow%20size%20largely%20comes%20down%20to%20personal%20preference%20and%20what%20fits%20your%20bed%20the%20best.%20Queen%20and%20king-size%20pillows%20comfortably%20fit%20on%20their%20coordinating%20mattress%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETraditional%20bed%20pillows%20follow%20a%20rectangular%20shape%2C%20but%20specialty-shaped%20pillows%20have%20grown%20in%20popularity%20to%20suit%20specific%20needs%20of%20different%20sleep%20styles.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-74965-20%26h%3Dd35ba14019889e4a4327185cf4cff073048cea1c1c10296c4a01a5bb7a9f965a%26postID%3D67ed6428b154b4859e632ce0%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fhow-to-choose-a-pillow%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Feliandelm.com%252Fproduct%252Fside-sleeper-pillow%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEli%20and%20Elm%20Side%20Sleeper%20Pillow%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20a%20unique%20crescent%20shape%20to%20provide%20support%20for%20side%20sleepers%20and%20reduce%20tension%20on%20your%20neck%2C%20while%20wedge%20pillows%20are%20useful%20to%20elevate%20the%20head%20or%20legs%20and%20can%20help%20with%20conditions%20like%20acid%20reflux%20or%20snoring.%20However%2C%20finding%20pillowcases%20for%20differently%20shaped%20pillows%20can%20be%20difficult%2C%20so%20keep%20that%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a92b4d1d-8044-4d46-8763-72e896696ce8%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20choose%20a%20pillow%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20choose%20a%20pillow%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Plush%20down%20pillow%20from%20Brooklinen%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20pink%20sheets%20and%20a%20cream%20headboard%20in%20a%20New%20York%20City%20apartment%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a13f4d2d66759f66fdde6c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Brooklinen%20Down%20Pillow%20is%20soft%20and%20comfortable%2C%20holding%20its%20shape%20even%20after%20years%20of%20regular%20use.%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Shinners%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20choosing%20a%20pillow%2C%20there's%20a%20plethora%20of%20details%20to%20consider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20key%20is%20to%20match%20the%20pillow%20to%20your%20unique%20sleep%20needs%3A%20your%20sleeping%20position%2C%20any%20neck%20or%20back%20pain%2C%20whether%20you%20sleep%20hot%2C%20and%20your%20material%20preferences%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Murray.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20works%20wonders%20for%20your%20best%20friend%20might%20leave%20you%20tossing%20and%20turning.%20So%20rather%20than%20chasing%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%26quot%3B%20pillow%20out%20there%2C%20look%20for%20the%20one%20that%20supports%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELearn%20about%20considerations%20like%20sleep%20position%2C%20comfort%2C%20care%2C%20value%2C%20and%20more%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d66491d5-8aba-4592-b2ef-4124794a81ce%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Sleep%20position%5C%22%3ESleep%20position%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20important%20factors%20to%20consider%20when%20choosing%20a%20pillow%20is%20your%20sleep%20position.%20Whether%20you%20sleep%20on%20your%20back%20or%20your%20side%20it's%20important%20to%20maintain%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspinehealth.org%2Farticle%2Fsleeping-and-the-spine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eneutral%20spinal%20alignment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20meaning%20that%20your%20spine%20is%20in%20its%20natural%20position%2C%20rather%20than%20being%20angled%20up%20or%20down.%20Your%20pillow%20plays%20a%20big%20role%20in%20promoting%20a%20healthy%20alignment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESide%20sleepers%2C%20the%20most%20common%20sleeping%20position%2C%20need%20a%20firm%2C%20supportive%20pillow%20with%20a%20higher%20loft.%20This%20pillow%20will%20cradle%20your%20head%20and%20stay%20supportive%20throughout%20the%20night.%20Side%20sleepers%20may%20prefer%20a%20firmer%20pillow%20material%2C%20like%20foam%20or%20latex.%20Dr.%20Robbins%20suggested%20that%20a%20side%20sleeper%20may%20also%20consider%20a%20double-gusset%20pillow%2C%20meaning%20there%20are%20two%20individual%20compartments%2C%20which%20can%20give%20a%20pillow%20more%20height.%20A%20gusset%20is%20an%20additional%20piece%20of%20fabric%20sewn%20into%20the%20pillow%2C%20which%20can%20be%20used%20to%20provide%20even%20more%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20sleepers%20are%20the%20Goldilocks%20of%20sleepers%2C%20needing%20a%20not-too-firm%2C%20not-too-soft%20feel.%20The%20loft%20should%20be%20middling%2C%20too%2C%20with%20a%20height%20tall%20enough%20to%20support%20the%20head%20while%20not%20being%20so%20tall%20as%20to%20crane%20the%20neck.%20To%20make%20sure%20back%20sleepers%20stay%20on%20their%20back%2C%20Dr.%20Robbins%20recommends%20a%20three-chamber%20pillow.%20%26quot%3BA%20back%20sleeper%20may%20consider%20a%20pillow%20with%20three%20chambers%2C%20one%20that%20runs%20along%20the%20bottom%20third%20of%20the%20pillow%2C%20that%20may%20be%20firmer%20to%20support%20the%20cervical%20spine%20while%20you%20sleep%2C%20then%20a%20middle%20chamber%20that%20supports%20the%20head%2C%20and%20a%20third%20upper%20chamber%20with%20a%20bit%20more%20fill%20than%20the%20center%20chamber%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Robbins%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20three%20compartments%20can%20provide%20support%20and%20help%20keep%20you%20on%20your%20back%20while%20you%20sleep.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20stomach%20sleepers%2C%20Dr.%20Robbins%20recommends%20a%20flat%20pillow%20with%20a%20low%20loft.%20In%20general%2C%20stomach%20sleepers%20should%20use%20pillows%20with%20a%20softer%20fill%2C%20like%20down%20or%20a%20down%20alternative%2C%20to%20ensure%20their%20spine%20stays%20aligned%20throughout%20the%20night.%20If%20one%20soft%20pillow%20isn't%20supportive%20enough%2C%20you%20can%20also%20stack%20multiple%20thin%20pillows%20for%20a%20more%20supportive%20feel%20while%20still%20promoting%20spine%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20you're%20a%20combination%20sleeper%3F%20%26quot%3BA%20responsive%2C%20medium-loft%20pillow%20that%20adapts%20as%20you%20switch%20positions%20is%20the%20perfect%20fit%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Murray.%20Since%20you'll%20be%20changing%20position%20throughout%20the%20night%2C%20a%20medium-loft%20pillow%20will%20keep%20you%20supported%20throughout%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2299d746fe-b616-4385-924a-9c47de939b2d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Firmness%5C%22%3EFirmness%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20your%20sleep%20position%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20consider%20how%20you%20want%20your%20pillow%20to%20feel.%20Pillows%20come%20in%20a%20range%20of%20feels%2C%20from%20plush%20to%20extra%20firm%2C%20and%20this%20is%20usually%20dependent%20on%20their%20material%20and%20fill%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20prefer%20a%20soft%2C%20cushy%20feel%2C%20down%20or%20down%20alternative%20pillows%20are%20a%20good%20choice.%20Hotel%20pillows%20are%20typically%20made%20with%20down%20or%20down%20alternative%2C%20so%20if%20you%20slept%20really%20well%20the%20last%20time%20you%20stayed%20at%20a%20hotel%2C%20you'll%20enjoy%20the%20feel%20of%20a%20down%20or%20down%20alternative%20pillow.%20If%20you%20like%20a%20soft%20pillow%20but%20need%20more%20support%2C%20down%20and%20down%20alternative%20pillows%20are%20perfect%20for%20stacking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20firm%2C%20supportive%20feel%2C%20choose%20a%20latex%20or%20memory%20foam%20pillow.%20Latex%20and%20memory%20foam%20are%20similar%20materials%2C%20but%20memory%20foam%20is%20better%20at%20contouring%20your%20head%20and%20neck.%20A%20firm%20pillow%20is%20generally%20a%20better%20choice%20for%20reliable%20support%20throughout%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e8e66467-8ff3-4baa-a681-9240ed865740%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Breathability%5C%22%3EBreathability%3C%2F