re%20really%20was%20accountability%20for%20vaccine%20safety.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20started%20discussing%20vaccinating%20the%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22409c0912-5224-48a9-ad26-c6e2007826ac%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20want%20other%20vaccine-hesitant%20parents%20to%20see%20my%20story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20the%20kids%20up-to-date%20with%20vaccines%20is%20a%20long%20process.%20It's%20still%20hard%20for%20me%20and%20them.%20Luckily%2C%20our%20new%20pediatrician%20is%20a%20great%20resource%20for%20creating%20a%20plan%20that%20works%20for%20us.%20They're%20behind%20a%20typical%20vaccine%20schedule%2C%20but%20we%20recently%20got%20their%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpediatrician-working-in-the-middle-of-texass-measles-outbreak-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20MMR%20vaccines%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20part%20because%20of%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharts-show-measles-spreading-in-us-states-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20measles%20outbreaks%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20the%20right%20choice%2C%20it%20was%20hard%20for%20me.%20I%20was%20proud%20that%20I%20overcame%20this%20challenging%20belief%20I%20used%20to%20have.%20But%20I%20also%20want%20parents%20like%20me%20to%20see%20it%20is%20OK%20to%20change%20their%20minds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2210d08d54-a707-4321-9df3-738625ce147c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChanging%20minds%20takes%20respect%20and%20time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20that%20felt%20very%20disingenuous%20to%20me%20in%20the%20past%20was%20when%20people%20advocating%20for%20vaccination%20said%20vaccines%20have%20no%20risk.%20Everything%20in%20life%20has%20risks%2C%20and%20it's%20important%20to%20acknowledge%20that.%20Today%2C%20I%20know%20the%20risk%20from%20vaccines%20is%20extremely%20minimal%20and%20comes%20with%20a%20huge%20reward.%20I%20put%20it%20in%20perspective%20by%2