Waqf%20Bill%20is%20against%20Indian%20Muslims%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashraf%20Ansari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20I%20am%20disheartened%20that%20I%20gave%20several%20years%20of%20my%20life%20to%20the%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20Qasim%20Ansari%20said%20in%20the%20letter%20in%20Hindi.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20say%20with%20due%20respect%20that%20millions%20of%20Indian%20Muslims%20like%20us%20had%20unwavering%20faith%20that%20you%20are%20the%20flag%20bearer%20of%20a%20purely%20secular%20ideology.%20But%20now%20this%20belief%20has%20been%20broken.%20Millions%20of%20dedicated%20Indian%20Muslims%20and%20workers%20like%20us%20are%20deeply%20shocked%20by%20the%20stand%20of%20JDU...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20The%20Waqf%20Bill%20is%20against%20Indian%20Muslims.%20We%20cannot%20accept%20it%20under%20any%20circumstances.%20This%20bill%20violates%20many%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20Through%20this%20bill%2C%20Indian%20Muslims%20are%20being%20humiliated%20and%20insulted...%20Neither%20you%20nor%20your%20party%20realises%20this.%20I%20regret%20that%20I%20gave%20many%20years%20of%20my%20life%20to%20the%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20Qasim%20Ansari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20an%20edge%20in%20terms%20of%20numbers%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Of%20the%20current%20strength%20of%20245%20MPs%2C%20the%20NDA%20has%20125%20-%20five%20more%20than%20the%20other%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20support%20for%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Union%20Minister%20and%20JD(U)%20leader%20Rajiv%20Ranjan%20(Lalan)%20Singh%20said%20the%20law%20is%20aimed%20at%20bringing%20transparency%20and%20ensuring%20the%20welfare%20of%20all%20sections%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JD(U)%20leader%20said%20attempts%20have%20been%20made%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20discussion%20to%20create%20an%20atmosphere%20that%20the%20bill%20is%20%26quot%3Banti-Muslim%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20it%20is%20not%20against%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWaqf%20is%20a%20sort%20of%20trust%20which%20is%20formed%20to%20work%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20Muslims.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20religious%20organisation...%20The%20trust%20has%20the%20right%20to%20do%20justice%20to%20all%20sections%20of%20Muslims%2C%20but%20that%20is%20not%20happening...%20Today%2C%20a%20narrative%20is%20being%20made.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20being%20criticised%2C%20if%20you%20do%20like%20him%20then%20do%20not%20look%20at%20him.%20But%20appreciate%20his%20good%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20accused%20opposition%20parties%20of%20creating%20a%20false%20narrative%20for%20political%20gain.%20He%20said%20the%20bill%20would%20improve%20the%20management%20of%20Waqf%20properties%20and%20ensure%20their%20income%20is%20properly%20used%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743699900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F7mmjj1mg_qasim-ansari-jdu_650x400_03_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjdu-leader-mohammed-qasim-ansari-resigns-over-partys-support-to-waqf-amendment-bill-8079334%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20key%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20leaders%20resigned%20from%20the%20party%20headed%20by%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20over%20the%20party's%20support%20to%20the%20passing%20of%20the%20Waqf%20Amendment%20Bill.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjdu-leader-mohammed-qasim-ansari-resigns-over-partys-support-to-waqf-amendment-bill-8079334%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Europe%20hopes%20for%20Trump%20tariffs%20deal%20but%20prepares%20for%20the%20worst%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743699698000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_