%20Siddharth%20was%20killed%20in%20the%20crash%2C%20but%20his%20actions%20ensured%20that%20no%20civilian%20lives%20were%20lost.%20His%20colleague%2C%20Manoj%20Kumar%20Singh%2C%20was%20injured%20and%20is%20currently%20receiving%20treatment%20in%20a%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddharth%20Yadav%2C%20the%20only%20son%20of%20Sushil%20and%20Neelam%20Yadav%2C%20had%20completed%20his%20training%20as%20a%20fighter%20pilot%20and%20joined%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20after%20passing%20the%20NDA%20exam%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20promoted%20to%20Flight%20Lieutenant%20just%20two%20years%20ago.%20His%20family%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Bhalkhi-Majra%20village%20in%20Rewari%2C%20was%20eagerly%20anticipating%20his%20wedding%2C%20which%20was%20scheduled%20for%20November%202.%20Siddharth%20had%20gotten%20engaged%20on%20March%2023%2C%20just%20days%20before%20returning%20to%20his%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20of%20his%20death%20has%20sent%20shockwaves%20through%20his%20family%20and%20the%20entire%20town%20of%20Rewari.%20Siddharth's%20father%2C%20Sushil%20Yadav%2C%20who%20is%20a%20retired%20Air%20Force%20personnel%20and%20currently%20working%20with%20LIC%2C%20said%20that%20his%20son's%20bravery%20in%20the%20face%20of%20danger%20would%20always%20be%20a%20source%20of%20pride.%20Siddharth's%20body%20is%20expected%20to%20arrive%20in%20Rewari%20on%20Friday%20morning%2C%20where%20it%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20his%20ancestral%20village%20for%20his%20final%20rites%20with%20full%20military%20honours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddharth%20was%20part%20of%20a%20family%20with%20a%20long%20tradition%20of%20military%20service.%20His%20great-grandfather%20served%20in%20the%20Bengal%20Engineers%20under%20the%20British%20regime%2C%20his%20grandfather%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Paramilitary%20Forces%2C%20and%20his%20father%20served%20in%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddharth's%20martyrdom%20has%20left%20his%20family%20and%20the%20community%20devastat