l%20consideration%2C%20has%20entrusted%20our%20Hon'ble%20Members%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20with%20the%20responsibility%20of%20exercising%20their%20conscience%20in%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20justice%2C%20harmony%20and%20the%20rights%20of%20all%20communities%2C%20should%20the%20Bill%20come%20up%20for%20voting.%20There%20is%20no%20Party%20Whip%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20has%20always%20upheld%20the%20principles%20of%20secularism%20and%20inclusivity%2C%20ensuring%20the%20rights%20of%20all%20communities.%20We%20deeply%20respect%20the%20diverse%20sentiments%20expressed%20by%20different%20sections%20of%20the%20Minority%20communities%20regarding%20the%20Waqf%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202024.%20Our%20Party%2C...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20%E0%AC%A1%E0%AC%BC%E0%AC%83%20%E0%AC%B8%E0%AC%B8%E0%AD%8D%E0%AC%AE%E0%AC%BF%E0%AC%A4%20%E0%AC%AA%E0%AC%BE%E0%AC%A4%E0%AD%8D%E0%AC%B0%20I%20Dr.%20Sasmit%20Patra%20(%40sasmitpatra)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsasmitpatra%2Fstatus%2F1907772496310579445%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%203%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20instance%20of%20a%20non-aligned%20party%20breaking%20ranks%20with%20the%20parties%20opposed%20to%20the%20bill.%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20opposition%20AIADMK%20and%20YS%20Jaganmohan%20Reddy's%20YSR%20Congress%20are%20so%20far%20standing%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20including%20them%2C%20the%20government%20has%20an%20edge%20in%20terms%20of%20numbers%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20%C2%A0Of%20the%20current%20strength%20of%20245%20MPs%2C%20the%20NDA%20has%20125%20-%20five%20more%20than%20the%20other%20side.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpening%20the%20gates%20for%20%26quot%3Bvoting%20on%20conscience%26quot%3B%20can%20only%20add%20to%20the%20government's%20strength.%20The%20BJD%20has%20seven%20members%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJD%20has%20always%20maintained%20what%20it%20called%20%26quot%3Bequal%20distance%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20but%20was%20known%20for%20providing%20%26quot%3Bissue-based%20support%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20case%20of%20contentious%20bills%20in%20parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%2C%20though%2C%20changed%20after%20last%20year's%20general%20and%20state%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patnaik's%20party%2C%20which%20had%20been%20ruling%20the%20state%20for%20three%20decades%20was%20decimated%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20failed%20to%20win%20any%20seat%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20BJP%20won%2020%20of%2021%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20and%2078%20of%20147%20assembly%20seats%20in%20Odisha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%2C%20Mr%20Patnaik%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%20BJP%20can%20no%20longer%20count%20on%20their%20support%20in%20parliament.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20reply%20to%20the%20Motion%20of%20Thanks%20to%20the%20President's%20address%20during%20the%20inaugural%20session%20of%20parliament%20after%20the%20election%2C%20the%20BJD's%20nine%20MPs%20joined%20the%20Opposition%20walkout%20over%20his%20remarks%20on%20Congress's%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20also%20tweaked%20its%20stand%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BOne%20Nation%20One%20Election%26quot%3B%20-%20which%20it%20once%20supported%20-%20called%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bfine%20print%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20proposal%20of%20the%20Kovind%20Committee%20adopted%20by%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20and%20suggested%20that%20the%20matter%20not%20be%20rushed%20like%20the%20farm%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743696480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fpdbqedho_naveen-patnaik-_625x300_21_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbased-on-conscience-n