%20that%20a%20statue%20of%20German%20philosopher%20and%20socialist%20leader%20Karl%20Marx%20will%20be%20installed%20in%20Chennai%20-%20a%20city%20that%20has%20served%20as%20a%20hub%20for%20the%20labour%20movement%20for%20over%20a%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20a%20suo%20motu%20announcement%20under%20Rule%20110%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20MK%20Stalin%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20Dravidian%20model%20government%20wishes%20to%20honour%20and%20pay%20tribute%20to%20the%20great%20global%20leader%20Karl%20Marx%20-%20a%20visionary%20thinker%20and%20revolutionary%20who%20formulated%20the%20philosophy%20of%20communism%20and%20gave%20the%20call%3A%20'Workers%20of%20the%20world%2C%20unite!'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20ongoing%2024th%20National%20Congress%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India-Marxist%20in%20the%20state's%20Madurai%2C%20which%20MK%20Stalin%20is%20scheduled%20to%20attend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMK%20Stalin%20hailed%20Karl%20Marx%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20influential%20thinkers%20in%20world%20history%2C%20whose%20ideas%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20numerous%20revolutions%20and%20societal%20changes%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20a%20time%20when%20no%20one%20wrote%20about%20India%2C%20it%20was%20Karl%20Marx%20who%20accurately%20analysed%20and%20documented%20the%20realities%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20recalled%20that%20in%201931%2C%20social%20reformer%20Periyar%20(E.V.%20Ramasamy)%20translated%20and%20published%20%26quot%3BThe%20Communist%20Manifesto%26quot%3B%2C%20authored%20by%20Marx%20and%20Friedrich%20Engels%2C%20into%20Tamil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20was%20widely%20welcomed%20by%20several%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECPI-M%20state%20Secretary%20P.%20Shanmugam%20revealed%20that%20the%20party's%20executive%20committee%20had%20formally%20requested%20the%20installation%20of%20a%20Marx%20statue%20and%20thanked%20MK%20Stalin%20for%20fulfilling%20their%20request.%20Dravidar%20Kazhagam%20President%20K.%20Veeramani%20described%20the%20decision%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20achievement%20of%20the%20Dravidian%20model%20government%26quot%3B.%20CPI%20State%20Secretary%20R.%20Mutharasan%20said%20the%20government's%20move%20would%20be%20remembered%20as%20a%20landmark%20in%20history.%20PMK%20founder%20Dr.%20S.%20Ramadoss%20called%20it%20a%20fitting%20tribute%20to%20Marx%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20comrade%20of%20labourers%26quot%3B%20and%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20respected%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20announcement%2C%20Stalin%20also%20revealed%20that%20the%20state%20government%20would%20construct%20a%20memorial%20building%20for%20the%20late%20All%20India%20Forward%20Bloc%20leader%20P.K.%20Mookiah%20Thevar%20at%20Usilampatti%20in%20Madurai%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20praised%20Mookiah%20Thevar%20for%20his%20early%20entry%20into%20politics%20and%20his%20close%20association%20with%20Pasumpon%20Muthuramalinga%20Thevar.%20MK%20Stalin%20recounted%20that%20Thevar%20was%20elected%20from%20the%20Periyakulam%20Assembly%20seat%20in%201952%20and%20continued%20to%20win%20elections%20from%20the%20Usilampatti%20constituency%20in%201957%2C%201962%2C%201967%2C%201971%2C%20and%201977.%20In%201971%2C%20he%20also%20won%20the%20Ramanathapuram%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%20MK%20Stalin%20highlighted%20Thevar's%20role%20during%20the%201967%20political%20transition%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20where%20he%20served%20as%20the%20pro-tem%20Speaker%20and%20administered%20the%20oath%20to%20newly%20elected%20MLAs.%20He%20also%20lauded%20Thevar's%20efforts%20in%20establishing%20educational%20institutions%20for%20the%20Thevar%20community%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20government%20colleges%20being%20set%20up%20in%20Kamuthi%2C%20Usilampatti%2C%20and%20Melaneelithanallur%20during%20the%20DMK%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3