p%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20tariffs%20--%20which%20include%2010%20percent%20across%20the%20board%20levies%20on%20imports%20and%20far%20steeper%20barriers%20on%20dozens%20of%20specific%20countries%2C%20including%20the%20top%20US%20trading%20partners%20--%20meant%20%26quot%3Bthe%20United%20States%20is%20no%20longer%20going%20to%20be%20cheated%20by%20foreign%20nations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeavitt%20appeared%20to%20rule%20out%20the%20possibility%20of%20Trump%20pulling%20back%20any%20of%20the%20tariffs%20before%20they%20are%20implemented%20over%20the%20coming%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20president%20made%20it%20clear%20yesterday%20this%20is%20not%20a%20negotiation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20always%20willing%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20phone%20to%20answer%20calls%2C%20but%20he%20laid%20out%20the%20case%20yesterday%20for%20why%20we%20are%20doing%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20countries%20around%20the%20world%20have%20had%2070%20years%20to%20do%20the%20right%20thing%20by%20the%20American%20people%20and%20they%20have%20chosen%20not%20to.%20They%20have%20ripped%20off%20American%20workers.%20They%20have%20taken%20our%20jobs%20overseas.%20The%20president%20is%20putting%20an%20end%20to%20that%20yesterday.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743687240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F3joc696s_donald-trump_625x300_03_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Foperation-over-patient-healing-donald-trump-on-us-economy-after-tariff-announcement-8079150%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Donald%20Trump%20acknowledged%20the%20shock%20brought%20by%20his%20tariffs%20onslaught%20Thursday%2C%20but%20said%20the%20US%20economy%2