ommission-investigation-13341259%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Alliance%20Calling%3A%20AIADMK-BJP%20May%20Have%20Finally%20Learnt%20A%20Hard%20Lesson%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20sight%20to%20behold%20when%20K.%20Annamalai%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20president%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20flogged%20himself%20with%20a%20rope%20in%20Coimbatore%20last%20December.%20The%20self-flagellation%20was%20an%20act%20of%20protest%E2%80%94prompted%20by%20the%20sexual%20assault%20of%20a%20student%20at%20Anna%20University%E2%80%94even%20if%20it%20left%20people%20wondering%20whether%20Annamalai%20was%20trying%20to%20catch%20the%20attention%20of%20his%20national%20leadership.%20For%2C%20he%20had%20let%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20down%2C%20failing%20to%20win%20a%20single%20seat%20from%20the%20state%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20even%20after%20mounting%20a%20high-decibel%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20the%20motive%20behind%20Annamalai's%20act%20of%20%E2%80%98penance'%2C%20it%20grabbed%20enough%20eyeballs%2C%20given%20as%20it%20came%20after%20his%20three-month%20absence%20from%20the%20state%20owing%20to%20a%20fellowship%20he%20was%20pursuing%20in%20the%20UK.%20It%20was%20rumoured%20that%20the%20central%20leadership%20of%20the%20BJP%20was%20disappointed%20with%20zero%20returns%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20especially%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20made%20as%20many%20as%20seven%20visits%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3ELost%20Opportunities%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrue%2C%20the%20BJP%20did%20make%20incremental%20gains%20in%20the%20state%20last%20year%2C%20with%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20cumulatively%20registering%2018.28%25%20votes.%20But%20a%20post-poll%20analysis%20showed%20that%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(AIADMK)%20could%20have%20fetched%20the%20combine%20as%20many%20as%2013%20out%20of%20the%2039%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20break%20also%20brought%20about%20a%20crucial%20change%20in%20Annamalai's%20attitude%20towards%20its%20once-ally%20AIADMK%2C%20the%20primary%20opposition%20party%20that%20he%20had%20relentlessly%20attacked%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20visibly%20transformed%20Annamalai%20has%20of%20late%20been%20training%20his%20guns%20on%20the%20ruling%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%2C%20along%20with%20the%20fledgling%20Tamilaga%20Vettri%20Kazhagam%20(TVK)%2C%20floated%20by%20superstar%20Vijay.%20During%20Annamalai's%20sabbatical%2C%20the%20TVK%20held%20its%20first%20political%20conference%20in%20Villupuram.%20More%20importantly%2C%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin%20was%20made%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20during%20his%20absence%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20political%20firmament%20underwent%20so%20much%20change%20that%20it%20may%20not%20be%20wrong%20to%20argue%20that%20Annamalai's%20novelty%20may%20have%20worn%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHints%20Of%20Rapprochement%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20an%20apparent%20political%20realignment%20on%20the%20cards%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20likely%20to%20resume%20its%20partnership%20with%20the%20AIADMK%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20assembly%20polls%20in%202026.%20Just%20last%20week%2C%20AIADMK%20leader%20Edappadi%20K%20Palaniswami%20(EPS)%20visited%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20in%20Delhi.%20Whereas%20EPS%20tried%20to%20play%20down%20the%20meeting%2C%20Shah%20acknowledged%20that%20talks%20for%20a%20formal%20alliance%20were%20indeed%20on.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnFor%20both%20the%20AIADMK%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20an%20alliance%20is%20necessary%20to%20stand%20a%20fighting%20chance%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20it%20should%20be%20remembered%20that%20in%20the%20previous%20assembly%20polls%20in%202021%2C%20the%20NDA%20led%20by%20the%20AIADMK%20had%20polled%20only%204.5%25%20fewer%20votes%20than%20the%20DMK%20front%20despite%20two-term%20anti-incumbency%20and%20the%20passing%20of%20the%20talismanic%20J.%20Jayalalitha.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20AIADMK%20has%20expelled%20rebels%20led%20by%20former%20chief%20minister%20O.%20Pannerselvam%20(OPS)%2C%20but%20it%20still%20very%20much%20remains%20a%20force%20to%20reckon%20with%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20both%20on%20account%20of%20its%20organisational%20heft%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98Two%20leaves'%20election%20symbol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20grown%20stronger%20in%20the%20interim%2C%20with%20a%20markedly%20improved%20showing%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20although%20the%20saffron%20party%20would%20find%20it%20tough%20to%20replicate%20that%20success%20in%20a%20state%20election.%20As%20for%20the%20AIADMK%2C%20which%20is%20undergoing%20an%20existential%20crisis%2C%20going%20back%20to%20the%20BJP%20wasn't%20a%20straightforward%20choice%20either.%20According%20to%20some%20reports%2C%20the%20Dravidian%20party%20was%20apparently%20exploring%20an%20alliance%20with%20Vijay's%20TVK%2C%20though%20the%20talks%20fell%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20New%20Kid%20On%20The%20Block%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay's%20TVK%20was%20unveiled%20in%20February%202024%2C%20but%20it%20did%20not%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20that%20followed%20a%20few%20months%20later.%20Now%2C%20with%20Vijay%20all%20set%20to%20wrap%20up%20his%20last%20film%E2%80%94his%20sixty-ninth%E2%80%94the%20superstar%20has%20given%20up%20on%20a%20lucrative%20acting%20career%2C%20while%20still%20in%20his%20prime%2C%20and%20turned%20to%20politics.%20It%20would%20indeed%20be%20far-fetched%20to%20assume%20that%20Vijay%20could%20replicate%20the%20success%20of%20matinee%20idol%20MG%20Ramachandran%2C%20but%20even%20so%2C%20he%20is%20the%20strongest%20lateral%20entrant%20to%20have%20come%20from%20Kollywood%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Vijaykanth%20in%202006%20or%20Kamal%20Haasan%20in%202021%E2%80%94not%20to%20forget%20Rajnikanth's%20political%20plunge%20that%20was%20not%20to%20be%E2%80%94Vijay%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20more%20methodical%20approach%20to%20his%20political%20debut.%20Whether%20the%20Vijay%20Makkal%20Iyakkam%E2%80%94the%20fan%20association%20that%20the%20actor%20converted%20into%20a%20social%20outfit%20in%202009%2C%20before%20metamorphosing%20into%20the%20TVK%E2%80%94could%20shape-shift%20into%20an%20out-and-out%20political%20party%20is%20a%20moot%20question.%20The%20actor%20had%20even%20said%20that%20he%20was%20willing%20to%20do%20business%20with%20other%20political%20parties%20and%20form%20a%20coalition%20under%20his%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20AIADMK's%20talks%20with%20the%20TVK%20fell%20apart%20solely%20over%20this%20issue%E2%80%94of%20projecting%20Vijay%20as%20the%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20in%202026.%20For%20a%20party%20that%20has%20ruled%20the%20state%20for%20over%20three%20decades%2C%20playing%20second%20fiddle%20to%20a%20new%20kid%20on%20the%20block%20wasn't%20exactly%20proper.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Difficult%20Friendship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20alliance%20between%20the%20AIADMK%20and%20the%20BJP%20isn't%20an%20easy%20thing%20to%20achieve%2C%20even%20with%20Annamalai%20finally%20taming%20his%20aggression.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20ruling%20DMK%20has%20been%20playing%20up%20emotive%20issues%20such%20as%20the%20Centre's%20three-language%20policy%20and%20the%20pending%20delimitation%20exercise%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20combat%20anti-incumbency.%20The%20AIADMK%20broadly%20subscribes%20to%20the%20same%20political%20ideology%20as%20the%20DMK%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20it%20cannot%20really%20afford%20to%20take%20a%20position%20completely%20at%20variance%20on%20these%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20an%20AIADMK-BJP%20alliance%2C%20if%20it%20does%20come%20to%20fruition%2C%20will%20have%20to%20be%20justified%20as%20a%20pragmatic%20political%20formation%2C%20one%20that%20focuses%20on%20more%20typical%20issues%20such%20as%20law-and-order%20and%20corruption.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20EPS%20is%20not%20keen%20to%20deal%20with%20Annamalai%20in%20an%20alliance%2C%20and%20it%20is%20assumed%20that%20the%20BJP%20would%20indulge%20the%20AIADMK%20at%20least%20on%20that%20count.%20Here's%20how...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20Equations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20both%20the%20Gounder%20and%20the%20Thevar%20communities%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20have%20aligned%20with%20the%20AIADMK.%20Jayalalitha's%20former%20aide%2C%20VK%20Sasikala%2C%20as%20well%20as%20former%20chief%20minister%20O.%20Palaniswami%E2%80%94now%20estranged%20from%20the%20AIADMK%E2%80%94hail%20from%20the%20Thevar%20community.%20It%20is%20expected%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20promote%20a%20Thevar%20leader%20such%20as%20Nagendran%2C%20now%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20party%20in%20the%20state%20legislative%20assembly%2C%20to%20replace%20Annamalai%20(Nagendran's%20base%20lies%20in%20the%20southern%20district%20of%20Tirunelveli).%20Of%20course%2C%20this%20would%20be%20rationalised%20as%20a%20move%20necessitated%20by%20social%20engineering%2C%20with%20both%20EPS%20and%20Annamalai%20hailing%20from%20the%20Gounder%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConversely%2C%20the%20BJP%20may%20push%20to%20get%20AIADMK%20rebels%20back%20into%20the%20NDA%20fold%20if%20the%20effort%20to%20unite%20the%20splinter%20factions%20with%20the%20mothership%20comes%20to%20naught.%20The%20saffron%20party%20will%20also%20try%20to%20build%20a%20grand%20NDA%20coalition%20beyond%20the%20AIADMK%20and%20the%20Vanniar%20outfit%2C%20the%20Pattali%20Makkal%20Katchi%20(PMK).%20As%20things%20stand%2C%20an%20alliance%20of%20the%20AIADMK%20and%20the%20BJP%20would%20dominate%20the%20DMK%20in%20western%20Tamil%20Nadu%20or%20the%20Kongu%20belt%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20once%20had%20the%20upper%20hand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20this%20wouldn't%20suffice.%20The%20alliance%20would%20have%20to%20shore%20up%20its%20base%20in%20southern%20and%20northern%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20combat%20the%20DMK%20and%20the%20TVK.%20There%20is%20a%20fourth%20player%20too%3A%20the%20Tamil%20Nationalist%20Naam%20Tamilar%20Katchi%20(NTK)%2C%20led%20by%20actor%20Seeman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIdeological%20Tightrope%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20alliance%20to%20stand%20any%20chance%20at%20winning%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20until%20the%202026%20election%20before%20it%20takes%20up%20the%20issue%20of%20delimitation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20double%20down%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98Hindi%20imposition'%20plank%20as%20well%2C%20but%20how%20much%20it%20will%20resonate%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20The%20ruling%20party%20is%20hoping%20that%20its%20welfare%20schemes%20for%20women%E2%80%94the%20free%20bus%20rides%20and%20monthly%20monetary%20allowance%20of%20Rs%201000%E2%80%94as%20well%20as%20its%20pitch%20for%20Tamil%20pride%20will%20see%20it%20through.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBe%20that%20as%20it%20may%2C%20there%20are%20some%20crucial%20chinks%20in%20the%20DMK's%20arsenal%2C%20which%20a%20formidable%20alliance%20can%20tap%20into%20if%20it%20acts%20effectively.%20There%20is%20visible%20anti-government%20sentiment%20among%20the%20state's%20urban%20middle%20class%20over%20a%20hike%20in%20power%20tariff%20and%20property%20taxes.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20roughly%20two%20million%20state%20government%20employees%20and%20pensioners%20are%20also%20miffed%20with%20the%20ruling%20government%20for%20not%20honouring%20its%20manifesto%20promise%20of%20hiking%20salaries%20and%20reverting%20to%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20AIADMK-BJP%20combine%20can%20mount%20a%20foolproof%20campaign%20anchored%20on%20bread-and-butter%20issues%2C%20victory%20may%20not%20be%20so%20unimaginable%20after%20all%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Anand%20Kochukudy%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20columnist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743686700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fvakte7jo_aiadmk-bjp_625x300_03_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fan-aiadmk-bjp-victory-isnt-as-unimaginable-as-it-seems-8078962%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20alliance%20between%20the%20AIADMK%20and%20the%20BJP%20isn't%20an%20easy%20thing%20to%20achieve%2C%20even%20with%20Annamalai%20finally%20taming%20his%20aggression.%20But%20it's%20not%20entirely%20impossible%20either.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fan-aiadmk-bjp-victory-isnt-as-unimaginable-as-it-seems-8078962%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20York%20Mayor%20Eric%20Adams%20drops%20out%20of%20Democratic%20primary%2C%20will%20instead%20run%20as...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1743686440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119946504%2Cimgsize-135820.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnew-york-mayor-eric-adams-drops-out-of-democratic-primary-will-instead-run-as-%2Farticleshow%2F119946519.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F119946519.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CMore%20than%2025%2C000%20New%20Yorkers%20signed%20my%20Democratic%20primary%20petition%2C%20but%20the%20dismissal%20of%20the%20bogus%20case%20against%20me%20dragged%20on%20too%20long%2C%20making%20it%20impossible%20to%20mount%20a%20primary%20campaign%20while%20these%20false%20accusations%20were%20held%20