ectivity%20was%20poor%20%E2%80%94%20we%20only%20had%20metre%20gauge%20trains%20to%20Ahmedabad%20and%20Delhi%2C%20and%20just%20one%20flight%20to%20Mumbai%20and%20one%20to%20Delhi.%20Apart%20from%20that%2C%20there%20was%20the%20prevalent%20patriarchy.%20People%20called%20me%20%3Cem%3Ebhabhiji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Edidi%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20Lakshmiji.%20They%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20my%20work.%20My%20attire%20was%20very%20different%20from%20the%20locals.%20I%20wore%20trousers%20and%20shirts%20in%20a%20place%20where%20women%20wore%20%3Cem%3Esaris%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20%3Cem%3Egoonghats%20%3C%2Fem%3E(veils)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20liberal%20in-laws%2C%20especially%20her%20mother-in-law%2C%20who%20worked%20in%20education%2C%20were%20a%20blessing.%20But%20the%20lack%20of%20ceramic%20design%20opportunities%20in%20Udaipur%20meant%20she%20had%20to%20carve%20a%20new%20path.%20She%20began%20organising%20artist%20camps%2C%20helping%20potters%20and%20artisans%20create%20new%20products%2C%20and%20soon%20started%20working%20with%20the%20NGO%20Seva%20Mandir%2C%20designing%20visual%20communication%20tools%20for%20rural%20communities.%20%E2%80%9CI%20could%20have%20moved%20back%20to%20Ahmedabad%20and%20pursued%20ceramics%2C%20but%20at%20the%20time%2C%20having%20a%20long-distance%20marriage%20just%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20considered%20acceptable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESketching%20periods%20into%20the%20picture%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELakshmi%E2%80%99s%20first%20real%20brush%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246267%2Fmenstrual-hygiene-kit-cloth-pads-avni-safepads-women-health-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenstrual%20health%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecame%20while%20developing%20training%20materials%20for%20non-literate%20communities.%20She%20realised%20the%20visuals%20she%20was%20drawing%20didn%E2%80%99t%20resonate%20with%20p